metadata.author: Yoto
metadata.description:
Grab your apron - its time to get baking! This activity card will have kids mixing, grating and kneading their way to scrumptious cheese scones in just 35 minutes, with instructions that they can follow at their own pace. From prepping ingredients to baking, eating, and tidying up, kids will have the opportunity to take the lead in the kitchen - with a mega side-serving of fun!   

Prepare for cheesy food jokes (sorry), snack-tastic music, a washing up tunes and more!  

Please note: this activity requires adult supervision and the use of an oven.  

Ingredients:  
Self-raising flour 
Baking powder 
Butter 
Cheese 
Milk  

This recipe takes around 35 minutes to complete, from preparing to bake to tucking in! Go through the steps at your own pace.
